caption: Table 1: Overview of resources used in our work.
description: This table lists the names of various software packages and libraries used in the research project, along with their respective references and licenses.  The packages cover various aspects of the workflow, including programming languages (Python), deep learning frameworks (PyTorch), numerical computation (NumPy, SciPy), data manipulation (Pandas), interactive computing (Jupyter), visualization (Matplotlib), and machine learning algorithms (Scikit-learn). The licenses indicate the terms under which these resources can be used and redistributed.
